        <h1 id="NMonsters" class="section-header-letter mm-header-letter-n" data-content-chunk-id="f54c1a60-e176-45cc-8da0-ad05d92d6a76"><strong>N</strong> <span style="color: #d4d0ce;" data-content-chunk-id="68f471a0-9326-4aef-9ee5-008cb1e9a330">|</span> Monsters</h1>
<h2 id="MonsterStatBlocks" data-content-chunk-id="303d42ff-3d14-4885-9853-84d96e75e0b4" class="heading-anchor"><a href="#MonsterStatBlocks" data-content-chunk-id="7815f094-ae4a-4028-ba18-19a90a553eab"></a>Monster Stat Blocks</h2>
<div id="_idContainer177" class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="c5381f45-86de-4788-88f0-2c7f2df2e437">
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="61ced9c3-8a7d-417e-ba17-302c06896749"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16963-nalfeshnee" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16963-tooltip">Nalfeshnee</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="00e6cd26-a14b-49bb-96db-5518459bd688">Large fiend (demon), chaotic evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f7bf682c-2967-4b17-ae46-268a744f04c3"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d7dc28d3-b7b9-4df4-87f3-0225c7fb7d18">Armor Class</span> 18 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="8f43871c-9e7c-44e8-aec9-f42216ea42c7"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d4695644-065a-41ad-b158-a22180e8cfca">Hit Points</span> 184 (16d10 + 96)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="09c0296e-e80c-4139-bd73-025940210adf"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="72735cb4-e8b7-4957-8dd8-f4e7ab00c027">Speed</span> 20 ft., fly 30 ft.</p>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores" data-content-chunk-id="a3508d42-1540-4cfa-9ccc-0e62bafc5498">
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-stat" data-content-chunk-id="5c06a1ed-01d6-4a3e-954a-c716ad5ba712">
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-heading" data-content-chunk-id="de2c72dc-ee7c-4dd4-906d-3d2b3b2aad00">STR</div>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="d500ebcd-9bb8-431b-80cc-2c5887e66e20"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="a3dce0fc-2b6d-428e-a39a-d56baf07da1e">21</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="7a7e25b3-5099-4a14-91f3-9465a6f58b8b">(+5)</span></div>
</div>
<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-stat" data-content-chunk-id="2b059015-2b2c-4937-af38-0a7749d2ec4a">
